{
  "answer": "**The work is *Viṣṇu Smṛti* (Vishnu Smriti), Chapter 43.**[^1]\n\nThis chapter enumerates a sequence of named hells (*narakas*) matching the query precisely: **Tāmisra (Darkness)**,[^2] **Andhatāmisra (Blinding Darkness)**,[^3] **Raurava (Howling)**,[^4] **Mahāraurava (Great Howling)**,[^5] **Kālasūtra (The Black Thread)**,[^6] **Saṃjīvana (Reviving)**,[^7] **Avīci (Waveless)**,[^8] **Kuḍmala (Bud)**,[^9] **Pūtimṛttika (Putrid Clay)**,[^10] **Lohaśaṅku (Iron Spike)**,[^11] **Kaṇṭakaśālmali (Thorny Silk-Cotton Tree)**,[^12] **Asipatravana (Forest of Sword-leaves)**,[^13] and **Lohacāraka (Iron Cage)**.[^14]\n\nThe durations are assigned as follows:  \n**\"In these, those who have committed heinous sins without performing *prāyaścitta* are tormented in succession for a Kalpa.\"** (Vi_43.23)[^15]  \n**\"Great sinners, for a Manvantara.\"** (Vi_43.24)[^16]\n\n[^1]: *Viṣṇu Smṛti*, Chapter 43, [/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/](/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/).\n[^2]: [/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-c760bd](/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-c760bd)\n[^3]: [/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-d9c8de](/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-d9c8de)\n[^4]: [/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-5fc195](/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-5fc195)\n[^5]: [/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-a020ea](/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-a020ea)\n[^6]: [/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-49fc10](/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-49fc10)\n[^7]: [/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-58cbfc](/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-58cbfc)\n[^8]: [/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-2d1bd6](/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-2d1bd6)\n[^9]: [/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-6dbb5f](/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-6dbb5f)\n[^10]: [/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-aaf2ef](/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-aaf2ef)\n[^11]: [/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-053f64](/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-053f64)\n[^12]: [/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-74f3c5](/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-74f3c5)\n[^13]: [/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-0fab36](/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-0fab36)\n[^14]: [/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-7f9b8e](/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-7f9b8e)\n[^15]: [/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-fc7b11](/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-fc7b11)\n[^16]: [/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-cd0885](/works/unknown-visnu-smrti-27f0d8/43/translation/#p-cd0885)",
